{"tid":2003093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫香港再出殯首輓曲作洗腦詞條藍屍簡嘉明係教育界之恥","createTime":"2020-05-05T14:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T12:06:15.000Z","uid":238451,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40e30625577382676323ffa3194388169036eeb8","tid":2003093,"uid":238451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"利申: 借友人AC出post<br />\n<br />\n香港再出發大聯盟主題曲《再出發》<br />\n<br />\n作曲: 鍾鎮濤   填詞: 簡嘉明<br />\n編曲：葉澍暉<br />\n監製：鄧智偉<br />\n總策劃：黃英豪  莊 嘉<br />\n<br />\n主唱：<br />\n周柏豪 菊梓喬 泳 兒<br />\n鄭俊弘 胡鴻鈞 許靖韻<br />\n銀河新星青年合唱團<br />\n (排名不分先後)<br />\n<br />\n大家屌作曲條破產佬同唱嗰啲垃圾之餘，唔好忘記作埋啲柒詞洗人腦嗰個簡嘉明都好大罪！<br />\n<br />\n條藍屍阿嬸以前喺女校教中文同文學，淨係識鳩讀課文，毫無教學熱誠，之後做咗陣教畜局，近幾年仲黐埋去麟伯度，以為自己做咗星，忽然富貴成日去Chanel d event，唔知阿第二任老公急症室醫生除咗戴手術帽之外仲有冇帽要戴呢🤗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMvLpT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMvLpT7.jpg&h=1e798f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hu4DKT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhu4DKT8.jpg&h=239329a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOd867u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOd867u.jpg&h=37916f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知自己樣柒兼老，影衰品牌，唔該Chanel PR唔好再搵阿嬋去event<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUU4FsF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUU4FsF.jpg&h=47aa7f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ytE4FsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FytE4FsH.jpg&h=fb4b471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收經仲學人youtube教化妝，好撚核突，幾十歲人教人用canmake<br />\n<br />\n利申：教畜受害者，學校好好，係條前教畜衰"},{"pid":"975203a369cfe54e42c70022ada82beb2c8d9127","tid":2003093,"uid":238451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"推野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b572077